tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE training_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  input_features VARCHAR(255),
  output_label VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE training_data (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	feature1 FLOAT,
	feature2 FLOAT,
	label INT
)

CREATE TABLE model_params (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	param_name VARCHAR(50),
	param_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE predictions (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	instance_id INT,
	prediction FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE evaluation_metrics (
    evaluation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    accuracy FLOAT,
    precision FLOAT,
    recall FLOAT,
    f1_score FLOAT
);
